{"tid":224494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁特稱港累內地有霧霾   前天文台長轟欠常識不重科學","createTime":"2017-05-01T06:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T00:34:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":127,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c825c86e55cc1016f32620fd863710acecd6ea66","tid":224494,"uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170501/large/1493618228_6ac7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170501%2Flarge%2F1493618228_6ac7.png&h=476bdb88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 政協副主席、特首梁振英早前接受電台訪問時曾表示，當吹南風時，香港污染物被指吹到廣東等城市造成霧霾，反之吹北風時，港人則埋怨廣東吹來污染物。香港天文台前台長李本瀅，日前在其網誌撰文反駁梁振英的言論，更批評「政府不重科學，欠科學常識」；現任天文台台長岑智明亦在facebook轉發此文章。<br />\n<br />\n李本瀅指，早前梁振英言論的潛意思是，在霧霾問題上，香港和廣東是對等的。不過，他指霧霾涉及污染量及氣象問題兩個因素。他續指，在污染量的問題，早前已有專家在報章上談及，香港本地產生的污染量較少，與內地產生的不對等。此外，他認為，香港和內地的霧霾情況，氣象條件也是不對等的。<br />\n<br />\n李本瀅解釋，香港在溫暖及炎熱季節時多吹南風，但由於空氣不穩定，令污染物向上空散去，往廣東而引致霧霾機會不高。換言之，引致廣東霧霾需有兩條件，一是吹南風，二是空氣要穩定。然而，他稱這兩個情況同時出現的機會偏低。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，總的來說，無論是污染量或氣象情況，由於風向及大氣穩定度等氣象條件並不配合，香港為廣東帶來霧霾條件機會不高，難以支持有關說法。他在文章最後更批評，「政府不重科學，欠科學常識，加上香港大學撤去數理兩科主修，在在都十分短視。另方面，已發展國家卻不斷加強 STEM（science, technology, engineering, mathematics）的教育，對比之下，我們是否相形見絀？」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170501/large/1493617120_a984.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170501%2Flarge%2F1493617120_a984.png&h=0731d3f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現任天文台台長岑智明亦在facebook轉發此文章。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170501/56636840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170501%2F56636840&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=9200795d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170501%2F56636840&h=e38e6358\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170501/56636840</a>"},{"pid":"ed4af8f5b9b894ccdb0f5949b735d8c9b0bd6472","tid":224494,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:23:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4928286b89c98e557b6025f14cc9a5b5fec258ee","tid":224494,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n689呢啲賣港賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124ea82de6debc1d47ace1ec5d662d2c51c9e27f","tid":224494,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:27:58.000Z","msg":"佢幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f0e275bdebb059756849d93a99b9f2790c933d","tid":224494,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街死啦屌"},{"pid":"9bc8ad5be84e25d54098349342a379eb90e4c78c","tid":224494,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"「美帝」杜林普嘅想法，都大同小異：被指輕視環境科學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3dc99a21e08e3a7968d250e7f45157212ead99c","tid":224494,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「政府不重科學，欠科學常識，加上香港大學撤去數理兩科主修，在在都十分短視。另方面，已發展國家卻不斷加強 STEM（science, technology, engineering, mathematics）的教育，對比之下，我們是否相形見絀？」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n是的。政府只重視如何賣港求榮。完。"},{"pid":"e0fa5d7e7e20d55fe35b12d16f8897bc0fe1b311","tid":224494,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:54:37.000Z","msg":"主要來源係東北689故鄉<br />\n廣東香港都係受惠者"},{"pid":"242791114580b4d82d41cedfe420f91910dbc08e","tid":224494,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「政府不重科學，欠科學常識，加上香港大學撤去數理兩科主修，在在都十分短視。另方面，已發展國家卻不斷加強 STEM（science, technology, engineering, mathematics）的教育，對比之下，我們是否相形見絀？」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n是的。政府只重視如何賣港求榮。完。</blockquote><br />\n政府專重科學 科研 就唔會死剩地產，金融<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924aae60cbebb196bb692e7ee0d7e8f0b4e8a0d7","tid":224494,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「政府不重科學，欠科學常識，加上香港大學撤去數理兩科主修，在在都十分短視。另方面，已發展國家卻不斷加強 STEM（science, technology, engineering, mathematics）的教育，對比之下，我們是否相形見絀？」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n是的。政府只重視如何賣港求榮。完。</blockquote><br />\n或者重蹈2000年代初期「科技港計劃」覆轍：<br />\n以 STEM 名義包裝，實際上係地產投資，而非科學教育。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9bfa01757bf786d04bc23cf8b206b4fbc06267","tid":224494,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"689幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6461f958105307d398018aba29b0671aa23ce824","tid":224494,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"現代指鹿為馬"},{"pid":"d4984f09926514fab02103f178b17e9d361b3d49","tid":224494,"uid":9250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"689個腦生係屎忽度"},{"pid":"1718cb8d452b94b96f8f091c7a10f1e07d359b32","tid":224494,"uid":960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"事實證明就算坐埋同一條船<br />\n只要有人侮辱佢嘅專業一樣會反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f613735e19d229561505aeff21884f0576695399","tid":224494,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:16: